<h3 id="contributions">Contributions</h3>
<ol>
  <li>We disentangled the task of persona-based dialogue generation into two sub-tasks: consistency understanding and dialogue generation.</li>
  <li>A BERT-based generative framework, BoB,was proposed for training persona-based dialogue models from limited data</li>
  <li>An unlikelihood training method with non-dialogue inference data was introduced to enhance persona consistency understanding</li>
</ol>

